reviewText: THE ONE AND ONLY UNTOUCHABLE SUPERSTAR OF THE WWE THERES NO COMPARISON TO HIM NO ONE CAN TOUCH A SOUL LIKE HIM..THANKS JOHN FOR ALL YOU DO..AMERICA..CENA IS #1..REGARDLESS!!!
